00077 void TemplateDataTest::testproperty_UserAttributes()
00078 {
00079         TemplateData temp;
00080         ParameterNameValueDefaultRequiredTypeList &params = temp.UserAttributes();
00081         ParameterNameValueDefaultRequiredType vparam;
00082 
00083         vparam.SetName(L"user-att-name-1");
00084         vparam.SetValueAscii("user-att-value-1");
00085         vparam.SetDefaultValueAscii("user-att-defaultvalue-1");
00086         vparam.RequiredFlag() = false;
00087         vparam.ControlledVocabulary().clear() ;
00088         params.push_back(vparam);
00089 
00090         vparam.SetName(L"user-att-name-2");
00091         vparam.SetValueText(L"user-att-value-2");
00092         vparam.SetDefaultValueText(L"user-att-defaultvalue-2");
00093         vparam.RequiredFlag() = true;
00094         vparam.ControlledVocabulary().clear()  ;
00095         params.push_back(vparam);
00096 
00097         vparam.SetName(L"user-att-name-3");
00098         vparam.SetValueText(L"user-att-value-3");
00099         vparam.SetDefaultValueText(L"user-att-defaultvalue-3");
00100         vparam.RequiredFlag() = false;
00101         vparam.ControlledVocabulary().push_back(L"control1");
00102         vparam.ControlledVocabulary().push_back(L"control2");
00103         params.push_back(vparam);
00104 
00105         CPPUNIT_ASSERT( temp.UserAttributes().size() == 3 );
00106 
00107         ParameterNameValueDefaultRequiredTypeList::iterator it = temp.UserAttributes().begin();
00108 
00109         CPPUNIT_ASSERT( (*it).GetName() == L"user-att-name-1" );
00110         CPPUNIT_ASSERT( (*it).GetValueAscii() == "user-att-value-1" );
00111         CPPUNIT_ASSERT( (*it).GetDefaultValueAscii() == "user-att-defaultvalue-1" );
00112         CPPUNIT_ASSERT( (*it).ControlledVocabulary().size() == 0 );
00113         CPPUNIT_ASSERT( (*it).RequiredFlag() == false);
00114         ++it;
00115         CPPUNIT_ASSERT( (*it).GetName() == L"user-att-name-2" );
00116         CPPUNIT_ASSERT( (*it).GetValueText() == L"user-att-value-2" );
00117         CPPUNIT_ASSERT( (*it).GetDefaultValueText() == L"user-att-defaultvalue-2" );
00118         CPPUNIT_ASSERT( (*it).ControlledVocabulary().size() == 0 );
00119         CPPUNIT_ASSERT( (*it).RequiredFlag() == true);
00120         ++it;
00121         CPPUNIT_ASSERT( (*it).GetName() == L"user-att-name-3" );
00122         CPPUNIT_ASSERT( (*it).GetValueText() == L"user-att-value-3" );
00123         CPPUNIT_ASSERT( (*it).GetDefaultValueText() == L"user-att-defaultvalue-3" );
00124         CPPUNIT_ASSERT( (*it).ControlledVocabulary().size() == 2 );
00125         CPPUNIT_ASSERT( (*it).RequiredFlag() == false);
00126 
00127         std::list<std::wstring>::iterator controllIt = (*it).ControlledVocabulary().begin();
00128         CPPUNIT_ASSERT( (*controllIt) == L"control1" );
00129         ++controllIt;
00130         CPPUNIT_ASSERT( (*controllIt) == L"control2" );
00131         ++it;
00132         CPPUNIT_ASSERT (it == temp.UserAttributes().end() );
